Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.38,0:00:05.62,japanese,,0,0,0,,(デイダラ)オイラの究極芸術だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.62,0:00:08.52,japanese,,0,0,0,,これから オイラは自爆する。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.52,0:00:10.49,japanese,,0,0,0,,《サスケ : コイツ…》
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.49,0:00:13.80,japanese,,0,0,0,,死んで オイラは芸術になる。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.80,0:00:19.43,japanese,,0,0,0,,今までにない爆発は この地に\N今までにない傷跡を残し➡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.43,0:00:25.11,japanese,,0,0,0,,そして オイラの芸術は\N今までにない称賛を受けるだろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.11,0:00:29.11,japanese,,0,0,0,,《トビ… 悪いな》
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.11,0:00:33.31,japanese,,0,0,0,,オイラの称賛のなか\Nテメエは確実に死ぬ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.45,0:00:38.02,japanese,,0,0,0,,半径10キロが爆発範囲だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.02,0:00:40.92,japanese,,0,0,0,,逃げきれやしねえぜ うん！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.92,0:00:47.63,japanese,,0,0,0,,さぁ 怯えろ…\N驚嘆しろ！ 絶望しろ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.63,0:00:51.23,japanese,,0,0,0,,泣きわめけ！ オイラの芸術は…。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.44,0:01:05.54,japanese,,0,0,0,,(デイダラ)喝！ 爆発だ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.82,0:01:41.82,japanese,,0,0,0,,(トビ)なっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.69,0:01:46.69,japanese,,0,0,0,,何だ あれは!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.50,0:02:00.50,japanese,,0,0,0,,(キバ)何だ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.27,0:02:06.61,japanese,,0,0,0,,(パックン)カカシ あれは？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.61,0:02:10.81,japanese,,0,0,0,,(カカシ)この感じ…\Nあのチャクラは 暁の…。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.75,0:02:18.12,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ヒナタ)な 何だろう…。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.12,0:02:21.62,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ナルト)行ってみるってばよ。\N(ヤマト)あぁ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.30,0:02:34.30,japanese,,0,0,0,,《香燐 : サスケ… まさか…》
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.98,0:02:42.91,japanese,,0,0,0,,《サスケのチャクラが感じられない！》
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.91,0:02:45.88,japanese,,0,0,0,,(水月)あの辺りは集合場所だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.88,0:02:47.98,japanese,,0,0,0,,まさか!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.49,0:02:55.16,japanese,,0,0,0,,って！ その まさかじゃないか!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.16,0:02:59.16,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ゼツ)デイダラのヤツ 自爆したな。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.16,0:03:01.96,japanese,,0,0,0,,トビは どこかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.27,0:03:09.57,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ゼツ)巻き添えだな\Nあの爆発の中にいただろうから。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.07,0:04:55.57,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ゼツ)デイダラが死んだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.57,0:04:58.48,japanese,,0,0,0,,最後は己で大爆発だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:05:02.71,japanese,,0,0,0,,(鬼鮫)あらら\Nまたメンバーが減っちゃいましたね。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.71,0:05:06.42,japanese,,0,0,0,,彼は 結構 強かったと思いますが。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.42,0:05:10.16,japanese,,0,0,0,,で どっちにやられたんです？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:14.03,japanese,,0,0,0,,サスケか 九尾の人柱力か？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.03,0:05:18.70,japanese,,0,0,0,,サスケだ。 ただしね…➡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.70,0:05:21.90,japanese,,0,0,0,,サスケも死んだみたいだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.27,0:05:27.11,japanese,,0,0,0,,道連れですか…。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.11,0:05:32.91,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ペイン)感謝するんだな イタチ。\Nデイダラが厄介払いをしてくれたんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.91,0:05:37.62,japanese,,0,0,0,,ん～ あと何か忘れてるような…。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.62,0:05:43.49,japanese,,0,0,0,,トビも死んだみたいだよ。 デイダラのヤツ\N見境なく爆発しやがった。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.49,0:05:49.63,japanese,,0,0,0,,そうそう トビでしたか…。 しかし\Nあの逃げ腰が逃げ遅れるとは➡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.63,0:05:53.06,japanese,,0,0,0,,相当 たいした術だったんですね。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.06,0:05:58.94,japanese,,0,0,0,,まぁいい。 あの程度の男なら\Nいくらでも補充は利く。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:06:01.41,japanese,,0,0,0,,デイダラは惜しかったが…。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.41,0:06:04.08,japanese,,0,0,0,,私は彼が好きでしたよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.08,0:06:07.95,japanese,,0,0,0,,陰鬱な この組織の場を\N和ませる能力なら➡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.95,0:06:10.95,japanese,,0,0,0,,トビも たいした能力者でしたがね。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.95,0:06:16.95,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレは行く。\Nせめて静かにデイダラを弔うとしよう。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.42,0:06:25.12,japanese,,0,0,0,,だったら ボクはトビの弔いを…。\N暇だな…。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.97,0:06:38.28,japanese,,0,0,0,,(水月)蛇の紋章が消えたら と…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.28,0:06:41.68,japanese,,0,0,0,,コイツをこうやって…。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.78,0:06:47.29,japanese,,0,0,0,,サスケの血をちょいと垂らして…。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.29,0:06:49.62,japanese,,0,0,0,,よし。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.62,0:06:52.62,japanese,,0,0,0,,口寄せの術！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.43,0:07:04.57,japanese,,0,0,0,,コ… コイツが大蛇丸の口寄せ マンダか。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.57,0:07:08.44,japanese,,0,0,0,,大蛇丸でさえ手を焼いていたコイツを\Nどうやって…。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.44,0:07:10.44,japanese,,0,0,0,,ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.44,0:07:14.94,japanese,,0,0,0,,《なるほど… 幻術か》
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.58,0:07:22.62,japanese,,0,0,0,,なんだ ボロボロじゃないか！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.62,0:07:25.76,japanese,,0,0,0,,誰とやり合ったんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.76,0:07:30.60,japanese,,0,0,0,,(マンダ)この… オレ様を…➡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.60,0:07:36.47,japanese,,0,0,0,,利用しやがって… このクソガキ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.47,0:07:42.61,japanese,,0,0,0,,その目…\Nその目で オレ様を操ったのか…。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.61,0:07:47.11,japanese,,0,0,0,,このオレ様を…。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.88,0:07:53.79,japanese,,0,0,0,,あ～ぁ 死んじゃったよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.79,0:07:57.76,japanese,,0,0,0,,マンダって あの大蛇丸の\Nいちばんのペットでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.76,0:08:03.76,japanese,,0,0,0,,動物は もっと大切にしなきゃ。\Nそれに ムリやり幻術かけてさぁ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.90,0:08:10.77,japanese,,0,0,0,,ギリギリだったからな…。\Nそんな余裕はなかった。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.77,0:08:12.77,japanese,,0,0,0,,(香燐)いた！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.77,0:08:14.91,japanese,,0,0,0,,やっぱりここか！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:18.41,japanese,,0,0,0,,急に チャクラが消えたから\Nどうしたのかと思えば➡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.41,0:08:20.35,japanese,,0,0,0,,飛んでたのか！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.35,0:08:22.58,japanese,,0,0,0,,マンダの中に入って➡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.58,0:08:27.09,japanese,,0,0,0,,時空間忍術で別空間へ\N飛んで逃げた… のはいいけど➡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.09,0:08:29.99,japanese,,0,0,0,,なんでそんなにボロボロなの？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.99,0:08:34.59,japanese,,0,0,0,,飛ぶ寸前に\Nマンダと一緒に爆風を受けた。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.59,0:08:39.09,japanese,,0,0,0,,相手は暁だ。\N思った以上のやり手でな…。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.77,0:08:45.44,japanese,,0,0,0,,《傷だらけのサスケも かっこいい》
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.44,0:08:49.11,japanese,,0,0,0,,とにかく少し休養をとらないとね。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.11,0:08:51.04,japanese,,0,0,0,,なぁ 香燐？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.98,0:08:56.85,japanese,,0,0,0,,だらしねえ！\Nそれでも大蛇丸をやった男かよ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.85,0:09:03.05,japanese,,0,0,0,,大蛇丸は もともと弱っていた。\Nそれだけの話だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.13,0:09:15.63,japanese,,0,0,0,,(鬼鮫)まだ やみませんねぇ。\Nこの時期に この地域で➡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.63,0:09:18.63,japanese,,0,0,0,,こうも降るのは\Nおかしいんですが。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.66,0:09:41.76,japanese,,0,0,0,,お体に障りますよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:50.17,japanese,,0,0,0,,冷酷なあなたが\N今 何を考えているのか➡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.17,0:09:52.14,japanese,,0,0,0,,それは わかりませんが➡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.14,0:09:55.77,japanese,,0,0,0,,ここからだと\N泣いてるように見えますよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.77,0:10:00.28,japanese,,0,0,0,,弟さんのことなら 残念でしたね。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.28,0:10:05.12,japanese,,0,0,0,,これで うちは一族は\Nあなた一人になってしまった。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.12,0:10:07.92,japanese,,0,0,0,,(イタチ)いや…。\Nん？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.29,0:10:16.96,japanese,,0,0,0,,アイツは死んでない。 それに…。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.96,0:10:20.66,japanese,,0,0,0,,どういうことです？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.97,0:10:29.97,japanese,,0,0,0,,(イタチ)雨が… やんだな。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.15,0:10:41.09,japanese,,0,0,0,,(サクラ)ナルト！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.09,0:10:43.99,japanese,,0,0,0,,みんな気になって\N駆けつけたようだね。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.99,0:10:45.92,japanese,,0,0,0,,何があったんだ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.92,0:10:49.86,japanese,,0,0,0,,サスケ君が さっきまで\Nここにいた形跡があるの。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.86,0:10:53.26,japanese,,0,0,0,,アイツのニオイが\Nかすかだが漂っている。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.26,0:10:56.60,japanese,,0,0,0,,それに いくつか\N他のニオイも残ってる。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.60,0:10:58.54,japanese,,0,0,0,,どういうことだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.54,0:11:01.44,japanese,,0,0,0,,(シノ)この地形の傷跡からして➡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.44,0:11:04.28,japanese,,0,0,0,,ここで 戦闘があったと\N考えられる。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.28,0:11:07.95,japanese,,0,0,0,,やっぱりだ。\Nこの 他のニオイのひとつは➡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.95,0:11:11.78,japanese,,0,0,0,,町で嗅いだ\Nサスケのニオイと混じってたヤツだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.78,0:11:14.82,japanese,,0,0,0,,どうやら サスケの近くについて➡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.82,0:11:19.12,japanese,,0,0,0,,一緒に行動しているヤツらが\Nいるようだ。 同伴者がいる。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.96,0:11:25.83,japanese,,0,0,0,,じゃあ あのとき…。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.83,0:11:31.47,japanese,,0,0,0,,おそらく サスケは\N小隊を組んで移動してたな。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.47,0:11:34.37,japanese,,0,0,0,,他の５つのニオイのうち ひとつは➡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.37,0:11:37.64,japanese,,0,0,0,,暁のデイダラと呼ばれていた男。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.64,0:11:40.14,japanese,,0,0,0,,え… アイツは自爆して➡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.14,0:11:43.65,japanese,,0,0,0,,カカシ先生の術で\N異空間に飛ばされたんじゃ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.65,0:11:46.15,japanese,,0,0,0,,どうやら 自爆に見せかけて➡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.15,0:11:49.05,japanese,,0,0,0,,逃げていた\Nということのようだな。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.05,0:11:50.99,japanese,,0,0,0,,で ヤツら暁は➡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.99,0:11:54.76,japanese,,0,0,0,,ツーマンセルで行動するから\N残りは３つ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.76,0:11:57.60,japanese,,0,0,0,,サスケは フォーマンセルで行動している。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.60,0:12:00.10,japanese,,0,0,0,,何人だろうと関係ねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.10,0:12:02.60,japanese,,0,0,0,,さっさと サスケのニオイを\N追うってばよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.60,0:12:05.44,japanese,,0,0,0,,それが ダメなんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.44,0:12:07.37,japanese,,0,0,0,,は？ なんで!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.37,0:12:10.31,japanese,,0,0,0,,ニオイが ここで なくなってる。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.31,0:12:12.31,japanese,,0,0,0,,どういうことだ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.45,0:12:19.28,japanese,,0,0,0,,こういう場合は サスケが爆発で\N跡形もなく消し飛んだか➡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.28,0:12:24.16,japanese,,0,0,0,,あるいは 時空間忍術で\N飛んだと考えるのが普通だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.16,0:12:26.86,japanese,,0,0,0,,時空間忍術？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.63,0:12:36.13,japanese,,0,0,0,,(キバ)どうやら 後者のようだな。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.13,0:12:40.97,japanese,,0,0,0,,今のオレは 犬以上に鼻が利く。\N見つけたぜ サスケ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.97,0:12:45.31,japanese,,0,0,0,,《忍犬以上の鼻とは\N成長したな キバ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.31,0:12:47.81,japanese,,0,0,0,,さすがは 犬塚家だ》
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.81,0:12:51.21,japanese,,0,0,0,,キバ 案内してくれ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.26,0:13:05.66,japanese,,0,0,0,,(小南)ペイン 来て。 彼が来たわ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.48,0:13:30.32,japanese,,0,0,0,,で サスケのほうは？\Nいい感じだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.32,0:13:34.89,japanese,,0,0,0,,写輪眼の力を\N十二分に発揮していた。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.89,0:13:37.80,japanese,,0,0,0,,あれは イタチ以上の眼になる。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.80,0:13:42.23,japanese,,0,0,0,,機は熟した。\Nヤツも覚悟は決まっているだろう。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.23,0:13:45.14,japanese,,0,0,0,,そう長くはないからな。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.14,0:13:48.11,japanese,,0,0,0,,じゃあ 九尾のほうは？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.11,0:13:50.37,japanese,,0,0,0,,お前が狩れ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.37,0:13:53.67,japanese,,0,0,0,,リーダーとして失敗は許さん。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.61,0:14:27.51,japanese,,0,0,0,,ヘッ\Nイタチをやるって言ってたくせに➡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.51,0:14:30.48,japanese,,0,0,0,,こんなザマじゃ\Nしばらくは動けねえぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.48,0:14:35.35,japanese,,0,0,0,,ここんところ 歩きづめだったから\Nちょうどいい。 休暇がとれる。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:39.49,japanese,,0,0,0,,テメエは休みっぱなしだったじゃ\Nねえか。 この貧弱野郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.49,0:14:41.89,japanese,,0,0,0,,よし 終わりだ。\N(水月)北アジトで➡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.89,0:14:44.30,japanese,,0,0,0,,なんにもしなかったキミには\N言われたくないね。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.30,0:14:49.50,japanese,,0,0,0,,なんだと コラ！ テメエやんのか オゥ。\Nああ やってやろうじゃねえか！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.50,0:14:51.54,japanese,,0,0,0,,いいかげんにしろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.54,0:14:56.67,japanese,,0,0,0,,水月 香燐。 それより\Nイタチの情報は集まったのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.67,0:14:59.58,japanese,,0,0,0,,ボロボロのテメエが\N偉そうに言ってんじゃねえよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:02.55,japanese,,0,0,0,,暁ってヤツらの情報は\Nいくつかつかんだが➡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.55,0:15:06.15,japanese,,0,0,0,,イタチについての\Nはっきりしたものはなかったよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.15,0:15:08.65,japanese,,0,0,0,,ウチは ゼロ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.99,0:15:13.89,japanese,,0,0,0,,ただ ヤツらは ある特定の人物➡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:17.60,japanese,,0,0,0,,特別なチャクラを持つ者たちを\N狙っているようだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.60,0:15:20.40,japanese,,0,0,0,,特別なチャクラ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.64,0:15:31.34,japanese,,0,0,0,,(重吾)オレは動物に語りかけ\N暁のアジトをいくつか把握した。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.75,0:15:39.15,japanese,,0,0,0,,その周辺では いつも大きく\Nイヤなチャクラを感じるらしい。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.15,0:15:42.12,japanese,,0,0,0,,動物たちは そう言ってる。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.12,0:15:47.73,japanese,,0,0,0,,へぇ 低能な動物たちも\Nチャクラを感じ取ることができるのか。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.73,0:15:52.83,japanese,,0,0,0,,いや 低能だからこそか。\Nまるで香燐みたいだね。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.30,0:15:58.40,japanese,,0,0,0,,っだと テメエ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.81,0:16:09.71,japanese,,0,0,0,,水月 テメエ 今度という今度は\N絶対許さねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.71,0:16:12.41,japanese,,0,0,0,,(水月)おい ちょっ… 待て。 おい。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.55,0:16:17.35,japanese,,0,0,0,,殺す。 殺したい。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.39,0:16:22.96,japanese,,0,0,0,,うぉ～っ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:26.76,japanese,,0,0,0,,うぉ～。\Nやばい。 重吾の殺人衝動が。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.76,0:16:30.06,japanese,,0,0,0,,サスケ 早くしろ。\N落ち着け 重吾。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.31,0:16:45.82,japanese,,0,0,0,,ハァ ハァ。\Nハァ ハァ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.82,0:16:48.72,japanese,,0,0,0,,ハァ ハァ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.72,0:16:51.52,japanese,,0,0,0,,す すまない。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.52,0:17:27.46,japanese,,0,0,0,,香燐が悪いんだぞ\Nギャーギャーと騒いで。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.46,0:17:29.93,japanese,,0,0,0,,あぁ？ お前だって。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.93,0:17:33.60,japanese,,0,0,0,,香燐 キミは そうやって\Nボクを挑発して➡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.60,0:17:35.53,japanese,,0,0,0,,何を企んでるんだい？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.53,0:17:37.47,japanese,,0,0,0,,前にも言ったと思うけど➡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.47,0:17:41.94,japanese,,0,0,0,,自分の目的のためにも\Nサスケから離れるつもりはないよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.94,0:17:45.61,japanese,,0,0,0,,べ 別に ウチは\Nなにも企んでるわけじゃなくて➡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.61,0:17:48.51,japanese,,0,0,0,,純粋に 水月 お前の気持を…。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.51,0:17:52.28,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレには… オレには サスケが必要だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.28,0:17:56.95,japanese,,0,0,0,,君麻呂の代わりになるのは…\Nサスケだけなんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.95,0:18:01.29,japanese,,0,0,0,,サスケは オレの檻になると\N言ってくれた。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.29,0:18:04.63,japanese,,0,0,0,,さっきのように オレの衝動を\N止められるのは➡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.63,0:18:07.53,japanese,,0,0,0,,今は サスケしかいない。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.53,0:18:10.50,japanese,,0,0,0,,でもね コイツはどうあれ➡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.50,0:18:13.97,japanese,,0,0,0,,その檻ってヤツには\N鍵なんてかかってないんだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.97,0:18:19.27,japanese,,0,0,0,,いつでも 誰でも抜け出せる。\Nなのにな…。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.16,0:18:40.86,japanese,,0,0,0,,間違いない こっちだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.27,0:18:49.61,japanese,,0,0,0,,ヤツのニオイは 動きを止めている。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.61,0:18:51.54,japanese,,0,0,0,,どうやら 潜伏しているようだぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.54,0:18:53.54,japanese,,0,0,0,,チャンスだな。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.48,0:19:00.48,japanese,,0,0,0,,《サスケ… お前への道が\Nつながったってばよ》
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:09.96,japanese,,0,0,0,,うずまきナルト… あれは\Nただのガキではなくなった。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.96,0:19:13.30,japanese,,0,0,0,,いまや たいそうな術を身につけ\N仲間も多い。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.30,0:19:15.97,japanese,,0,0,0,,簡単には いかんぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.97,0:19:19.64,japanese,,0,0,0,,一撃で あの角都の命を\N二つ削った。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.64,0:19:24.91,japanese,,0,0,0,,ターゲットをおそるべしとする\N言葉は ちりに等しい。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.91,0:19:28.21,japanese,,0,0,0,,ペインは 負けたことがないのだから。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.25,0:19:34.95,japanese,,0,0,0,,フフッ… まっ それもそうだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.59,0:19:45.93,japanese,,0,0,0,,話は終わりだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.93,0:19:49.80,japanese,,0,0,0,,他のメンバーに\N残りの人柱力を急がせろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.80,0:19:51.80,japanese,,0,0,0,,わかっている。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.80,0:19:58.51,japanese,,0,0,0,,いよいよだ… 我らが\N目的を達成するのも あとわずか。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.95,0:20:11.62,japanese,,0,0,0,,そうなれば すべてが\N本来の形に戻るのだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.24,0:20:39.24,japanese,,0,0,0,,写輪眼の本当の力が…\Nこの うちはマダラの力が！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.93,0:20:54.80,japanese,,0,0,0,,また 空が鳴き出した。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.80,0:20:58.50,japanese,,0,0,0,,ペイン あなた…。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.63,0:22:49.93,japanese,,0,0,0,,(カプリコ)開け ベルパラソの狩人 サマグィ。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.77,0:22:55.37,japanese,,0,0,0,,レイラの娘を仕留めてこい。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.57,0:00:05.17,english,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my ultimate art...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.10,0:00:08.23,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I will detonate myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.87,0:00:10.10,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.27,0:00:13.77,english,,0000,0000,0000,,With death, I will become art.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.80,0:00:15.83,english,,0000,0000,0000,,This never-before-seen explosion\Nwill leave
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.87,0:00:19.43,english,,0000,0000,0000,,a never-before-seen scar\Non this land.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.67,0:00:24.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,And...! My art will win\Nnever-before-seen admiration!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.87,0:00:28.30,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sorry, Tobi...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.50,0:00:29.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.40,0:00:33.43,english,,0000,0000,0000,,In the midst of my admiration,\Nyou will definitely die!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.70,0:00:38.07,english,,0000,0000,0000,,An explosion that will cover\Na ten-kilometer radius...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.10,0:00:41.07,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.73,0:00:43.77,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, tremble with fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.80,0:00:46.87,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Be in awe! Despair!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.07,0:00:49.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Scream!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.17,0:00:50.83,english,,0000,0000,0000,,My art is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.70,0:01:05.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,An explosion!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.93,0:01:41.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.07,0:01:46.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.10,0:02:00.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What the--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.07,0:02:06.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakashi, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.03,0:02:10.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,This chakra...\NIt's that Akatsuki member...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.20,0:02:17.80,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.00,0:02:20.33,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.90,0:02:21.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.93,0:02:27.70,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.33,0:02:33.43,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sasuke... It can't be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.17,0:02:42.83,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't sense Sasuke's chakra!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.20,0:02:45.87,english,,0000,0000,0000,,That's near our rendezvous point...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.47,0:02:47.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me he's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.27,0:02:54.67,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! It's just as I feared!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.37,0:02:59.17,english,,0000,0000,0000,,That Deidara...\NHe blew himself up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.93,0:03:01.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Tobi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.50,0:03:09.17,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably dead...\NHe was within the blast range...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.93,0:04:52.93,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Disappearance\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.97,0:04:55.30,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Deidara is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.33,0:04:58.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, he went out with a bang.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.57,0:05:02.70,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh dear.\NAnother member has been lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.83,0:05:06.10,english,,0000,0000,0000,,And I thought he was\Npretty strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.00,0:05:09.87,english,,0000,0000,0000,,So? Which one did him in?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.40,0:05:13.97,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke? Or the Nine-Tails' Jinchuriki?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.03,0:05:15.80,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It was Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.07,0:05:17.50,english,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.23,0:05:21.50,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like Sasuke is dead too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.47,0:05:26.63,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Deidara took Sasuke down\Nwith him, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.20,0:05:29.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You should feel grateful, Itachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.63,0:05:32.43,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Deidara did you a favor\Nand got rid of your problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.23,0:05:37.60,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... I feel like\Nwe've forgotten something...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.80,0:05:40.00,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like Tobi is dead too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.17,0:05:43.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,That Deidara detonated himself\Nwithout regard for his surroundings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.67,0:05:46.07,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah yes, Tobi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.27,0:05:53.07,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It must've been quite a jutsu\Nif that chicken was unable to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.67,0:05:58.67,english,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter...\NHe can easily be replaced.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.20,0:06:01.17,english,,0000,0000,0000,,The loss of Deidara, however,\Nis unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.60,0:06:04.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I liked Tobi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:08.07,english,,0000,0000,0000,,When it came to lightening the mood\Nin our rather gloomy organization,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.10,0:06:11.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Tobi was quite talented.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.33,0:06:12.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.00,0:06:15.97,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall mourn Deidara's death in silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.53,0:06:22.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll mourn for Tobi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.17,0:06:24.07,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You must really be bored, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.40,0:06:37.20,english,,0000,0000,0000,,When the crest of\Nthe snake vanishes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.87,0:06:41.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...I do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.13,0:06:46.77,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Add a drop of Sasuke's blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.50,0:06:48.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.83,0:06:51.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Summoning Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.53,0:07:02.70,english,,0000,0000,0000,,S-So, this is Orochimaru's\NSummoning Jutsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.87,0:07:04.23,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Manda...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.70,0:07:06.83,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Orochimaru had trouble\Ncontrolling this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.87,0:07:08.20,english,,0000,0000,0000,,How did Sasuke manage to...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.77,0:07:14.90,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see. He used genjutsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.50,0:07:21.80,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, you're a mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.20,0:07:24.77,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Who did you fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.67,0:07:29.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You...had the nerve...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.60,0:07:33.07,english,,0000,0000,0000,,to use me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:36.33,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You damned brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.60,0:07:42.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Those eyes...you controlled me...\Nwith those eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.50,0:07:46.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I...of all...people...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:53.80,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh-ohh, he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.37,0:07:57.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't Manda Orochimaru's\Nfavorite pet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.10,0:08:00.70,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You ought to treat animals better...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:03.80,english,,0000,0000,0000,,And the whole manipulation\Nwith the genjutsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:10.20,english,,0000,0000,0000,,There wasn't time to think.\NI had no choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.10,0:08:12.20,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.17,0:08:14.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured you'd be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:18.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Your chakra suddenly disappeared,\Nso I wondered what had happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.17,0:08:19.60,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you transport yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.43,0:08:22.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You hid yourself inside Manda,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.43,0:08:26.93,english,,0000,0000,0000,,then used the Transportation Technique\Nto escape into another dimension...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.27,0:08:29.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,So why are you in such bad shape?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.13,0:08:34.10,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Just before escaping,\Nwe both got hit by the blast wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.63,0:08:36.10,english,,0000,0000,0000,,My opponent was one of the Akatsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.63,0:08:38.60,english,,0000,0000,0000,,He was stronger than I expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.00,0:08:45.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sasuke all cut up and bruised\N{\i1}is also hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.90,0:08:50.17,english,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, he needs time to rest.\NRight, Karin?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.33,0:08:53.80,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahem! How pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.03,0:08:56.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,And you call yourself the man\Nwho killed Orochimaru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.33,0:08:59.83,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Orochimaru was already weakened\Nto begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.63,0:09:02.10,english,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.67,0:09:13.83,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It just won't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.87,0:09:18.30,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange to have this much rain\Naround here at this time of year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.40,0:09:41.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll ruin your health.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.97,0:09:52.30,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what someone as cold as you\Ncould be thinking about right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.47,0:09:55.43,english,,0000,0000,0000,,But from here,\Nyou look as though you are crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.70,0:10:00.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bad about your younger brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.33,0:10:04.70,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You are now the sole survivor\Nof the Uchiha clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.40,0:10:06.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.53,0:10:07.43,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.90,0:10:16.70,english,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not dead. Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.90,0:10:19.90,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.07,0:10:28.67,english,,0000,0000,0000,,The rain...has stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.53,0:10:40.70,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.03,0:10:43.60,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it caught all our attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.10,0:10:45.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.87,0:10:49.00,english,,0000,0000,0000,,There are signs that Sasuke\Nwas just here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.27,0:10:53.07,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very faint,\Nbut his scent still lingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.17,0:10:56.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I also detect other scents.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.13,0:10:58.63,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.93,0:11:03.70,english,,0000,0000,0000,,From the damage to the terrain,\NI'd say there was a battle here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.50,0:11:08.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it! One of the other scents\Nbelongs to that fellow in town
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.50,0:11:10.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,on whom I detected Sasuke's scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.73,0:11:11.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.13,0:11:17.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like there are others\Ntraveling alongside Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.97,0:11:19.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,He has a companion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.10,0:11:23.80,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, back there...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.13,0:11:28.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probable that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.07,0:11:31.30,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke has formed his unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.80,0:11:37.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the five other scents belongs\Nto Deidara from Akatsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.73,0:11:40.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't he the one\Nwho self-destructed
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.50,0:11:43.20,english,,0000,0000,0000,,and was transported to another dimension\Nby your jutsu, Sensei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:48.30,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems he faked\Nhis own death to escape...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.17,0:11:54.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,The Akatsuki operate in two-man cells,\Nso there are three left.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.97,0:11:57.30,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke is moving with\Na four-man cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.50,0:11:59.67,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares how many there are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.07,0:12:02.30,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get moving and\Ntrace Sasuke's scent!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.77,0:12:05.23,english,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.63,0:12:07.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.03,0:12:10.10,english,,0000,0000,0000,,The scent stops here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.97,0:12:12.23,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.07,0:12:16.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Usually in a situation like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.50,0:12:19.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,either Sasuke was blasted to bits\Nby the explosion...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.60,0:12:23.97,english,,0000,0000,0000,,or Sasuke used\Nthe Transportation Technique to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.50,0:12:26.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Transportation Technique...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.23,0:12:35.17,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably the latter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.43,0:12:39.23,english,,0000,0000,0000,,My sense of smell is keener\Nthan a dog's right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.33,0:12:40.80,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I've found Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.57,0:12:43.80,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A nose that's sharper than\N{\i1}the ninja hounds...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.83,0:12:45.33,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Impressive, Kiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.37,0:12:47.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just what I would expect\N{\i1}from a member of the Inuzuka clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.77,0:12:50.70,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiba, lead the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.47,0:13:03.20,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, Pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.07,0:13:05.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,He's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:28.60,english,,0000,0000,0000,,And...what of Sasuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.90,0:13:30.43,english,,0000,0000,0000,,He's coming along nicely...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:34.60,english,,0000,0000,0000,,He was using the Sharingan's power\Nto his fullest...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.77,0:13:37.20,english,,0000,0000,0000,,His eyes will surpass Itachi's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.07,0:13:42.30,english,,0000,0000,0000,,The time has come.\NHe must be ready as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.70,0:13:44.67,english,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, he doesn't have much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.70,0:13:47.87,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what about the Nine-Tails?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.40,0:13:52.90,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You hunt it.\NAs leader, failure is not an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.10,0:14:15.30,english,,0000,0000,0000,,INN OKOSHI
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.90,0:14:27.83,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Hah! You talked about killing Itachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.87,0:14:30.30,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to move around\Nfor some time in that condition!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.90,0:14:35.43,english,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been moving nonstop lately.\NIt's a good chance to rest up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.70,0:14:39.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,All you've done is rest,\Nyou feeble punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.23,0:14:40.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,There, finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.57,0:14:42.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't do a thing at\Nthe northern hideout,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.77,0:14:44.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,so don't start telling me\Nwhat to do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.33,0:14:47.50,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Wanna make something of it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:49.43,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.47,0:14:50.90,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.53,0:14:56.60,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Suigetsu, Karin...\NHave you gathered data on Itachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.07,0:14:59.77,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in no shape to act so bossy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.37,0:15:03.43,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I've picked up some tips\Nabout Akatsuki,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.47,0:15:06.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,but nothing specific\Nabout Itachi himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.00,0:15:08.30,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I got zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.03,0:15:13.67,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems they're targeting\Nspecific people though...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.37,0:15:17.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,People with special chakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.50,0:15:20.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Special chakra...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.83,0:15:31.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I did some talking to animals and\Nlocated a number of Akatsuki hideouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.70,0:15:36.10,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems they always sense
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.13,0:15:38.90,english,,0000,0000,0000,,a powerful, unpleasant chakra\Naround each area.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.87,0:15:41.60,english,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what the animals have told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.27,0:15:47.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, even simpleminded animals\Ncan sense chakra, eh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.13,0:15:50.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe it's because\Nthey're simpleminded...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.77,0:15:52.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like you Karin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.20,0:15:57.90,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say, you jerk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.57,0:16:10.20,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Suigetsu! This time,\Nyou're not getting away with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.23,0:16:12.70,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... W-Wait...hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.17,0:16:17.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill... I want to kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.23,0:16:19.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,- Huh?\N- Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.90,0:16:23.20,english,,0000,0000,0000,,INN OKOSHI
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.77,0:16:26.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot! Jugo's killing impulse is loose!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.60,0:16:28.17,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke! Hurry it--!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.37,0:16:30.00,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Jugo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.83,0:16:50.80,english,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.30,0:17:27.33,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault, Karin.\NScreaming and making such a fuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.60,0:17:29.70,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You too...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.93,0:17:33.60,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You constantly try to provoke me, Karin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.63,0:17:35.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.60,0:17:37.50,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.53,0:17:41.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't intend to leave Sasuke\Nfor my own reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.73,0:17:45.43,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm not up to anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.47,0:17:48.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just trying to test your...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.60,0:17:51.80,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I...I need Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.57,0:17:56.43,english,,0000,0000,0000,,The only one who can\Nreplace Kimimaro...is Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.47,0:18:00.60,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke said he would\Nbecome my cage...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.63,0:18:05.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, only Sasuke can\Nstop my urges,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.57,0:18:07.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,like he did earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.83,0:18:13.97,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Still... I don't know about her,\Nbut our cages are unlocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.30,0:18:19.00,english,,0000,0000,0000,,We can escape anytime we wish.\NAnd yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:40.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure of it. It's this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.03,0:18:49.20,english,,0000,0000,0000,,From his scent,\NI can tell he's stopped moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.23,0:18:51.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems he's resting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.73,0:18:53.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It's our chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.90,0:19:00.60,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sasuke...\N{\i1}Our paths have finally crossed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.83,0:19:09.33,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto Uzumaki...\NHe's no longer just a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.13,0:19:12.10,english,,0000,0000,0000,,He has now mastered\Na formidable jutsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:13.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,and has many comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.57,0:19:15.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be easy.
